      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "That’s right, under that Bronco body is a 2011 Ford F-150 SVT Raptor chassis plus powertrain. Actually, it’s from supercharged ",
